{"tid":1699873,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講哂，今晚開唔開花？定尊重死者家屬意願？","createTime":"2019-11-08T08:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T08:41:50.000Z","uid":34676,"like":32,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec978e30965da0cec7fae4ec473d5eb6f39eb618","tid":1699873,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"「各位街坊手足，對於周同學的離去，我們已無法再用其他言語表達我們的傷痛。<br />\n<br />\n但周同學的家人十分希望安靜渡過最沉痛的一晚，所以除了簡單悼念活動外，其他活動請避免，他們也想各手足安全。願各位平平安安回家，生者堅強，逝者安息。<br />\n<br />\nForm: 將軍澳tg channel」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今日悼念，安靜咁俾周同學離開，尊重死者家人，開花容後打算。<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今日乃重大契機，機不可失，為周同學出口氣"},{"pid":"7c89633859712171bee945bbba89fd8764ac8890","tid":1699873,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"988fcd704f7c38b55e444f54523f7ad99085435e","tid":1699873,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:16:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea58b450cf6a7839f6d40c8294c5b33a66a6cb89","tid":1699873,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"十八區集合悼念 上花<br />\n不衝擊 不裝修"},{"pid":"88f49ef3084d4bc8c1988b69005270df601432aa","tid":1699873,"uid":34676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"推，想問問大家意見？定係各有各做，要悼念既去悼念，要開花既就開花。"},{"pid":"4964a83d31f3ad0e5221e252058be54b8ae1d094","tid":1699873,"uid":132352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"我都好亂 又開花 又悼念 又連儂"},{"pid":"cc3ac7d285843206b72d1363cf028a6e53b1673e","tid":1699873,"uid":65091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"問問問，次次都開幾廿個正負皮po, 戇鳩鳩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5a1e8bdb4bec4be255a6d69df8f01ab3d24fb8","tid":1699873,"uid":3467